high_descs: Turn around and go near the countertop.
Take the mango from the table.
And then go near the fridge.
Put the mango on the refrigerator and cooled it.
Take it from the refrigerator and go near the sink.
Then placed the mango on the table near the sink.
anns.task_desc: Placed the Mango on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the corner of the kitchen countertop.
Pick up the round yellow mango next to the pot.
Walk around the counter to the fridge.
Place the mango into the fridge, shut the door, then retrieve the mango and shut the door again.
Go back to the counter, near the sink.
Place the mango on the counter next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cool a round yellow mango in the fridge and place it on the kitchen counter near the sink.

high_descs: Turn left to walk to the countertop.
Pick up the yellow mango next to the larger pot.
Head right to walk to the fridge.
Put the mango on top of the fridge to cool and take it out.
Turn around to face the sink on the counter.
Place the mango on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled Mango on the Sink.
